BEGIN_PGML
In the second half of the game, that same team scored [`[$coefs[1]]`] penalty shots, [`[$coefs[3]]`] long field goals, and [`[$coefs[5]]`] short field goals. How many points did they earn during the second half?

[_]{$two}{20}

END_PGML

Section::End();

############################################################
# Section
